([NotesComponentProblem Problem] < [NotesComponents index] > [NotesComponentAmr Amr])

= Simulation Component =

A `Simulation` defines and manages a computational astrophysics [NotesComponentProblem Problem] or an ensemble of related [NotesComponentProblem Problem]s.  Invokes [NotesComponentTimestep Timestep] to advance the [NotesComponentProblem Problem](s), and may call the [NotesComponentParallel Parallel] component to manage the high-level parallelization of multiple [NotesComponentProblem Problem]s in an ensemble.
